        cy:command (K): get	.action-select
        cy:command (K): assert	expected **<select.form-control.action-select>** to have value **--Select a fruit--**
                        Actual: 	"--Select a fruit--"
                        Expected: 	"--Select a fruit--"
        cy:command (K): get	.action-select
        cy:command (K): select	apples
        cy:command (K): get	.action-select
        cy:command (K): assert	expected **<select.form-control.action-select>** to have value **fr-apples**
                        Actual: 	"fr-apples"
                        Expected: 	"fr-apples"
        cy:command (K): get	.action-select-multiple
        cy:command (K): select	[apples, oranges, bananas]
        cy:command (K): invoke	.val()
        cy:command (K): assert	expected **[ Array(3) ]** to deeply equal **[ Array(3) ]**
                        Actual: 	["fr-apples","fr-oranges","fr-bananas"]
                        Expected: 	["fr-apples","fr-oranges","fr-bananas"]
        cy:command (K): get	.action-select
        cy:command (K): select	fr-bananas
        cy:command (K): assert	expected **<select.form-control.action-select>** to have value **fr-bananas**
                        Actual: 	"fr-bananas"
                        Expected: 	"fr-bananas"
        cy:command (K): get	.action-select-multiple
        cy:command (K): select	[fr-apples, fr-oranges, fr-bananas]
        cy:command (K): invoke	.val()
        cy:command (K): assert	expected **[ Array(3) ]** to deeply equal **[ Array(3) ]**
                        Actual: 	["fr-apples","fr-oranges","fr-bananas"]
                        Expected: 	["fr-apples","fr-oranges","fr-bananas"]
        cy:command (K): get	.action-select-multiple
        cy:command (K): invoke	.val()
        cy:command (K): assert	expected **[ Array(3) ]** to include **fr-oranges**
"
]
